metadata.name: Linda
metadata.description:
Linda loves her childhood friends. Linda misses her childhood friends... She didn't talk to them since The Doctor said they are IMAGINARY...
But sometimes she ''forgets'' to take a SPECIAL PILL and then in her deep deep dreams Linda takes a sip of her secret sweet and spicy BESTFRIENDSFOREVER cocktail...and call them all. After a long long colourful conversation full of sparkles and flying mashrooms she wakes up fresh and happy, full of power to handle one more day in REAL LIFE
